  "text": "In 1948 Van Krevelen and Hoftijzer [CITATION_1] developed the first approximate analytical relation based on film theory for absorption with irreversible second order chemical reaction. The developed relation is implicit in nature and was developed for equal diffusivities of reactants but later applied for other diffusivity ratios also. The Van Krevelen and Hoftijzer [CITATION_2] correlation is considered as the pioneering work in the development of approximate analytical models. Their expression is given as shown in eq. [CITATION_3] ",
